articles.title: Unlocking Potential: Natural Gas Poised for Upside Movement - FX Empire
articles.description: Natural gas positions itself for an upward move, supported by a bullish consolidation and a confirmed reversal on the weekly chart.
articles.content: An initial higher target is in the 2.77 price area. That price level is indicated by both the 38.2% Fibonacci retracement as well as the completion of a rising ABCD pattern (D) as marked on the chart… [+1245 chars]
